<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="6Mar1939"><font color="red">6 March 1939</font> <i>NLGC</i> (from Charles M. Saffer to Paul L&eacute;on): Two months ago, I sent to Mr James Joyce, through you, at his request, a six page typewritten letter concerning the parallelism between the development of his writing and the advance of science. </div>
